title: Be My Victim and Other Strange Tales From The Cape
description:
The Cape Province is the oldest province with many tales. Many of them are true...


A helpless twelve year old girl becomes the victim of a kidnapping that will lead her to a life of sexual slavery. Or is she helpless?


When a cyclist is forced to overnight in a farmhouse, he has a strange dream. The same dream the occupant of the house just told him about. Coincidence?


Where there is sin, there is always room for one more.


"A house in the middle of a sulfur mine? I don't believe that...why only the devil would have a house in the middle of a sulfur mine...haha"


Little Page HAS to walk over the dark field with the low bushes to reach her father's house. She is scared, but there is no other way. Luckily her mother is with her. But will that help her?
